---
title: Pair with Me
---
%article
  %h1 Pair with Me
  %p Inspired by Avdi Grimm's talk at Ancient City Ruby 2013, I want to pair with other developers. Send me a note using the form below and lets find a time to work together.
  %form#contactForm(method='post' action='/' style='display: none;')
    %input(type='hidden' name='return_url' value='http://jonallured.com/pair/thanks.html')
    %p#jsNote You must have JavaScript enabled to use this form.
    .wrapper
      .field.text
        %label(for='name') Name:
        %input#name.required(type='text' name='message[name]')
      .field.text
        %label(for='email') Email:
        %input#email.required.email(type='text' name='message[email]')
      .field.text
        %label(for='subject') Subject:
        %input#subject(type='text' name='message[subject]')
      .field.textarea
        %label(for='name') Message:
        %textarea#body.required(name='message[body]')
      .action
        %input(type='submit' value='Submit')
:javascript
  $('#jsNote').hide();
  $('form#contactForm').attr('action', 'http://contact.jonallured.com/');
  $('form#contactForm').show();
